  "commit_message": "solver: cache concretization results immediately after solve (#51931)\n\nPreviously, the concretization cache was written after all post-processing\n(finalization, hash assignment, patching, splicing, etc.), which meant that\ncached results were fully concrete and could not have post-processing\nsteps re-applied when packages changed. This moves the cache write to\nimmediately after the solve and flag reordering, but *before* finalization.\n\nThis requires care with serialization, because specs at cache",
